<topic id="filters-outliner">
  <title>Outline Filters</title><prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords><indexterm>XML Outline View<indexterm>outline filters</indexterm></indexterm></keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>The following actions are available in the <ph product="editor author"
          ><uicontrol>Settings</uicontrol> menu of the Outline view</ph><ph
        product="editorEclipse authorEclipse"><uicontrol>View menu</uicontrol> of the Outline
        view</ph>:<dl id="ouline-filters-dl">
        <dlentry id="filter-returns-exact-dlentry">
          <dt><uicontrol>Filter returns exact matches</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>The text filter of the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view returns only exact
            matches.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/CaretUpdateOff16.png" id="image_km1_vft_tr"/>Selection
              update on caret move</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Available when editing in <uicontrol>Text</uicontrol> mode. Controls the
            synchronization between <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view and source document. The
            selection in the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view can be synchronized with the caret
            moves or the changes in the editor. Selecting one of the components from the
              <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view also selects the corresponding item in the source
            document.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="outline-flat-presentation-mode"
          conref="relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view.dita#relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view/outline-flat-presentation-mode">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry
          conref="relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view.dita#relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view/outline_show_comments">
          <dt/>
